data.description: Beautiful Cedar-wrapped Rambler on 2.38 wooded acres with Park-like setting. Large 26x16 Deck adjacent to the 16x12 Screened Porch, long private Paved Driveway leads to a 2-car attached Garage. Conveniently located near Routes 20 & 621, only 12 miles from Route 3 at Chancellorsville, & only 5 mins to Lake Orange. Open Living & Dining with Cathedral Ceilings. Country Kitchen, Ceiling Fans.
